            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Caelius <expan><abbr>Saco</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>milis <note>sic</note> alae |(miliariae) <lb n="4"/>Flaviae Domitianae <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>civi</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> Romanae <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/>Brita<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>nicae</abbr></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex cert="low">ro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex cert="low">estamento</ex></expan> pater <expan><abbr>Sac</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im Hauptbild oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Brustbild eines bartlosen Mannes in paenula. Im Zwischenbild Reiter mit Schild und Lanze. Datierung: Beinamen der Ala. Z. 1: AE-Ligatur; Z. 3: AE-Ligatur; Z. 4: AE-, AE-Ligaturen; Z. 5: AE-Ligatur; Z. 6: AE-Ligatur. Die AE-Ligaturen mit sehr kurzen Querhasten. (B): AE 1940: Z. 1: Calius; Z. 3: milis ala II; Z. 4: Flavia Domitiana; Z. 5: Romana; Z. 6: Britannica. (B): RIU; Lőrincz: Z. 1: Cae[l]ius. Ubl: Z. 1: Ca[e]lius.</p>
            </div>
